    <h1 id="general" class="page-header">General</h1>

    <p class="faq-question"> CO2IN? How do I say that? <p>
    <p class="faq-answer"> CO<sub>2</sub> Coin = see-oh-too-coin. </p>

    <p class="faq-question"> Yet another cryptocurrency? Why should I care about CO<sub>2</sub>IN? </p>
    <p class="faq-answer"> After the BETA stage, 20&#37; of all CO<sub>2</sub>IN in existence will be set aside solely for the purchase of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_offset">carbon offsets</a>. As more people participate in the CO<sub>2</sub>IN ecosystem and the coin's value grows so too will the value of emissions offsets that can be purchased. </p> 

